<item>
            <title>[LU-15282] Don&apos;t hold a spin locks during space alloc (rr policy)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15282</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;alloc_rr now is broken during an lod landing because spin lock release during loop.&lt;br/&gt;
once no enough stripes during allocation loop reset will be to the wrong position.&lt;br/&gt;
Lets fix and replace this with atomic operations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
